children.subject: I wish CS 162 also have this T_T
Can I still join the class if I didn't see that form until now

history.content:
Due to departmental budget restraints (@16046) and high demand for the course, we may not be able to enroll everyone interested in the course. When processing the waitlist, we will try to prioritize students who need CS 161 to graduate. Note that we will not un-enroll anyone who is currently enrolled.

If you need to take CS 161 in spring 2022, please fill out this form (regardless of if you're on the waitlist now or not): https://forms.gle/hdKoU9DveaqYmdkt5

We don't know how many students we'll be able to add to the class, so we can't guarantee a spot if you fill out the form. We'll keep you posted as we learn more. If you have any questions, feel free to leave a follow-up on this post or send an email to cs161-staff@berkeley.edu.

Thank you for your understanding! We will do our best to support as many students as we can.

~CS 161 Spring 2022 Staff
